        "evidence": "<p>Probability of survival = 1/(1 + <em>e</em><sup>-b</sup>)</p>\n<p>where&nbsp;b = b<sub>0</sub> + b<sub>1</sub>(<calculator id=\"683\">RTS</calculator>) + b<sub>2</sub>(<calculator id=\"1239\">ISS</calculator>) + b<sub>3</sub>(A)</p>\n<p>A is determined by the following:</p>\n<table border=\"0\" style=\"border-collapse: collapse; width: 100%; height: 66px;\">\n<tbody>\n<tr style=\"height: 22px;\">\n<td style=\"width: 47.440636200716845%; height: 22px;\"><strong>Age, years</strong></td>\n<td style=\"width: 47.440636200716845%; height: 22px;\"><strong>A</strong></td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"height: 22px;\">\n<td style=\"width: 47.440636200716845%; height: 22px;\">&le;54</td>\n<td style=\"width: 47.440636200716845%; height: 22px;\">0</td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"height: 22px;\">\n<td style=\"width: 47.440636200716845%; height: 22px;\">&gt;54</td>\n<td style=\"width: 47.440636200716845%; height: 22px;\">1</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<p>Values for the coefficients:</p>\n<table border=\"0\" style=\"border-collapse: collapse; width: 100%;\">\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"width: 97.65625px;\"><strong>Trauma type</strong></td>\n<td style=\"width: 97.609375px;\"><strong>b<sub>0</sub></strong></td>\n<td style=\"width: 97.609375px;\"><strong>b<sub>1</sub></strong></td>\n<td style=\"width: 97.609375px;\"><strong>b<sub>2</sub></strong></td>\n<td style=\"width: 97.609375px;\"><strong>b<sub>3</sub></strong></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"width: 97.65625px;\">Blunt</td>\n<td style=\"width: 97.609375px;\">-1.2470</td>\n<td style=\"width: 97.609375px;\">0.9544</td>\n<td style=\"width: 97.609375px;\">-0.0768</td>\n<td style=\"width: 97.609375px;\">-1.9052</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"width: 97.65625px;\">Penetrating</td>\n<td style=\"width: 97.609375px;\">-0.6029</td>\n<td style=\"width: 97.609375px;\">1.1430</td>\n<td style=\"width: 97.609375px;\">-0.1516</td>\n<td style=\"width: 97.609375px;\">-2.6676</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>",
