        "logic": "var calc_output = [];\n\n// Declare vars\n\nvar traumatype = parseFloat(traumatype);\nvar rts = parseFloat(rts);\nvar iss = parseFloat(iss);\nvar a = parseFloat(a);\n\nvar b;\n\nif (traumatype == 0) {\n  b = -1.2470 + 0.9544*rts + -0.0768*iss + -1.9052*a;\n}  else {\n  b = -0.6029 + 1.1430*rts + -0.1516*iss + -2.6676*a;\n}\n\nvar prob_survival = 1/(1 + Math.exp(-b)) * 100;\n\ncalc_output.push({\n  name: 'mini',\n  value: prob_survival.toFixed(1),\n  value_text: '%',\n  message: 'Probability of survival'\n});\ncalc_output.push({\n  name: 'Probability of survival',\n  value: prob_survival.toFixed(1),\n  value_text: '%',\n  message: 'Probability of survival'\n});\n  ",
